The delegation from the Commonwealth of Kentucky to the Southern Dairy Compact Commission, as established in Article III of the compact, set out in KRS 260.670, shall be composed of five (5) members appointed by the commissioner of agriculture as follows:
Two (2) members shall represent the Commonwealth at large;
One (1) member shall be a dairy farmer engaged in the production of milk at the time of appointment or reappointment;
One (1) member shall represent consumers of milk; and
One (1) member shall represent fluid milk processors.
